{"tid":1434334,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"回應：「香港示威已經走在失敗之路上」","createTime":"2019-08-08T17:45:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T05:09:54.000Z","uid":272592,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d99db1c315cdbaf8004d9ad5e20b309f305401b1","tid":1434334,"uid":272592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:45:34.000Z","msg":"(原文：<br />\n香港示威已經走在失敗之路上<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1432756\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1432756</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n為左唔想大家睇咁多頁又TLDR，加上有絲<br />\n打建議我開新po，咁就開新po回應一下)<br />\n<br />\n廢話少講<br />\n小弟暫時剩係諗到以下嘅point<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong><em>1. 善用民間記者會</em></strong></span><br />\n- 可以用多啲數字、法律理據等譴責克警<br />\n- 針對權貴/建制派發放嘅假消息，喺記者會上用事實反駁（未諗到例子，歡迎巴絲幫手加）<br />\n<br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">2. 所有人（和理非、勇武派）<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">必須</span></span> 立即upgrade 所有裝備同埋提高警覺性</span></span></em></strong><br />\n- 冇full gear同埋保護自己嘅能力就咪撚上前線啦屌你老母<br />\n- 食花生嘅唔撚該你地咪撚上前線啦，陣間你地落單又要前線救你地，仲未計入面有好多鬼<br />\n- 咁撚多懶人包教哂你地點樣鎖電腦鎖電話保護自己啲設備，你地都唔撚去做？（我就唔撚信你地個個都有做足）<br />\n<br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: blue;\">3. 和理非要做多嘢，再做多啲</span></em></strong><br />\n- 轉台器買撚左未呀？有冇撚用過呀？<br />\n- 說好的罷食罷買呢？可唔可以畀多少少掙扎？（我知不過都放埋喺度）<br />\n- 有冇幫你地啲屋企人手轉走哂啲CCTVB呀？<br />\n- （未諗到，歡迎補充）<br />\n<br />\n原諒我講嘅嘢大部分都係老調重彈，但係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>如果你地連最撚基本嘅嘢都做唔足做唔好，你點撚樣話畀人地聽你地個決心有幾大？你地對唔對得住畀克警拉嘅手足？</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>求下你地，真係求鳩你地呀，一人做多一步好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好正評/負評/睇完就算好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span>"},{"pid":"2f4776c22838ca03cac9dd41d1620fcc7078fd3a","tid":1434334,"uid":268538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:46:38.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0371180b8a4e3e45deb498cee276f0111b7f5af","tid":1434334,"uid":179402,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:53:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/OjM9aG3xZKk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FOjM9aG3xZKk&d=2tiv49EdsLtkS%2FsM0tMlCDMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=95a7cf04\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/OjM9aG3xZKk</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/F74MRhonX28\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FF74MRhonX28&d=2tiv49EdsLtkS%2FsM0tMlCDMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=994e115c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/F74MRhonX28</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n有youtube喇！！！！！！！！！！！！<br />\n<br />\n幫手派出去 推上報<br />\n<br />\n今次拍片者冇事 下個好難講<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42c1b91bd4f41e1158b3616cc33c2eda830d52bf","tid":1434334,"uid":272592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d0371180b8a4e3e45deb498cee276f0111b7f5af","tid":1434334,"uid":179402,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:53:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/OjM9aG3xZKk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FOjM9aG3xZKk&d=2tiv49EdsLtkS%2FsM0tMlCDMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=95a7cf04\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/OjM9aG3xZKk</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/F74MRhonX28\" data-sr-